Package project3

Class Fulltime

java.lang.Object
project3.Employee
project3.Fulltime
Direct Known Subclasses:
Management
public class Fulltime
extends Employee
Fulltime class is an extension of the Employee class. It is for full time employees and holds an employees annual salary.
Author:
Shane Hoffman, Michael Li
